# 🛠️ Project -wide set -up guide

Welcome to **{{ project_name }}**

This page ties together the platform -specific installation notes and the
standard, cross -platform tasks you should perform **after** the initial
clone.

| Platform | Quick link | Typical use -case |
|----------|-----------|------------------|
| Linux / macOS | [local -linux](linux.md) | Primary workstation or university laptop |
| Windows 10/11 + WSL 2 | [windows -wsl](windows.md) | Keep a POSIX tool -chain without dual -booting |
